               <p>(M.) He was a second time indicted, for that <rs id="t17690510-9-off63" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17690510-9-off63" type="offenceCategory" value="violentTheft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17690510-9-off63" type="offenceSubcategory" value="highwayRobbery"></interp>
               he, together with two other persons unknown, did assault 
                     
                        <persName id="t17690510-9-victim152" type="victimName">
                           Richard 
                           Smith 
                        <interp inst="t17690510-9-victim152" type="surname" value="Smith"></interp>
