                     </persName>
                      
                   on the King's highway, and took from his person a pair of silver shoe buckles, value 8 s. a nine shilling piece, a thirteen-and-sixpenny piece, twelve guineas, four half guineas, and four quarter guineas, his property
            </rs>, <rs id="t17690510-9-cd64" type="crimeDate">April 13</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17690510-9-off59 t17690510-9-cd64"></join>
